description: Break ups are usually a very stressful business. Especially when you have to leave your now ex-partner's flat. That was exactly the case of this guy. I met him shortly after he got kicked out. The poor dude was just walking around a park, trying to figure out what to do. He didn't want to go back to his difficult father, who lived in a small town. The guy wanted to stay in Prague and enjoy life. No problem, I was ready to help. The guy was 19 years old and really good looking so you can imagine what I wanted in exchange. I took him to my place and paid him a lot of cash. He tried very hard to make me happy and was doing great for a first timer. He whored himself out but also made enough money to rent his own flat and start a new, better life. And I got what I wanted. What a perfect conclusion!
title: Czech Hunter 491
